data.question: What is the maximum quantity for purchase?
How can I get the discount?
data.answer: Whenever there is any kind of sales/discount offers in our products, you can easily see it in web banner and will provide you a coupon to redeem while carting our products.

data.question: Can I cancel my order if needed?
data.answer: The order can be canceled by manually contacting our customer service. But if any products are already dispatched from our location then you are liable to pay the return delivery charges.

data.question: How do I contact customer support?
data.answer: If you have any queries a member of our team will always be happy to help. You can simply contact us on (+)977-1-4411302 and mail us at cs@dalle.com.np
